.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
City: hannover, miami, marseilles, nizza, hamburg
Nationality: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
Cigar: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
Hobby: rock-climbing, gardening, writing, drawing, sudoku
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Nationality:english == City:hannover
2. Nationality:spanish == Pet:dog
3. Hobby:rock-climbing == City:miami
4. Nationality:ukranian == Hobby:gardening
5. City:miami is to the right of City:marseilles
6. Cigar:old-gold == Pet:snails
7. Cigar:kools == City:nizza
8. Hobby:writing is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:chesterfields is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Cigar:kools is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Cigar:lucky-strike == Hobby:drawing
13. Nationality:japanese == Cigar:parliaments
14. Nationality:norwegian is to the left or right of City:hamburg

.:: Answer ::.
